<h2 id="section-top">Ear, Nose &amp; Throat</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=1431">Lewisham and Greenwich NHS Trust</a>
</p>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="service-locations clear">
<div class="panel edit-box">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p class="address">Ear, Nose and Throat (ENT) Department<br/>020 8333 3000 ask for extension 8092</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent6702457e2ba7462bbf50e04f765b6228">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="ENT at LHT" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=1848"/>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>The Trust provides comprehensive ear, nose and throat (ENT) services at University Hospital Lewisham, and also delivers outpatient clinics at Queen Mary’s Hospital in Sidcup and Queen Elizabeth Hospital in Woolwich.</strong></p>
<p>Services include our highly-regarded <a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/surgery/ear,_nose__throat_ent/voice_clinic.aspx"><strong>Voice Clinic</strong></a>, which provides comprehensive treatment to patients with voice disorders and receives referrals from across the UK and abroad.</p>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong>What services are available?</strong></p>
<p>In addition to our general ENT services, we deliver a wide range of specialist clinics, including:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/surgery/ear,_nose__throat_ent/voice_clinic.aspx">Voice Clinic</a></strong> </li>
<li>Otology (Hearing) Clinic </li>
<li>Rhinology (Nose and Sinus) Clinic </li>
<li><a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/surgery/ear,_nose__throat_ent/one-stop_clinic_for_neck_lumps.aspx"><strong>One-stop Clinic for Neck Lumps</strong></a> </li>
<li>Two Week Wait Clinic </li>
<li><a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/surgery/ear,_nose__throat_ent/combined_ent__dermatology.aspx"><strong>Dermatology, Facial Plastic &amp; Reconstructive Surgery Clinic</strong></a> </li>
<li>Children's ENT</li>
</ul>
<p>Through the above clinics, we are able to treat a variety of conditions, including adenoids, hearing loss, facial pain, nasal obstruction, sinusitis, sleep disorders, tinnitus, tonsillitis and much more.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Further information</strong></p>
<p>For further information, including clinic times, referral details and key staff, please <strong><a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/surgery,theatres__anaesthetic/ent.aspx">visit the ENT section of our website</a></strong>.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
